    "body": "Using `clone` rather than `clone_from` is less efficient for non-trivial types. Why not work on making `zip` optimize here if that's the real problem? At the very least, it should avoid `zip` while continuing to use `clone_from` because right now it's a micro-optimization at the expense of being a macro-pessimization.\n",
